px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0;"><strong>Education</strong>. Each of the =
&#8220;flourishing cultures&#8221; Lehrer examined &#8220;pioneered new for=
ms of teaching and learning.&#8221; In Florence, it was the rise of the app=
rentice-master model; in Elizabethan England, it was the government&#8217;s=
