e royal support for his odd tragedies.&#8221; Wealthy benefactors gave crea=
tives room to flourish. (This one sits between exogenous and endogenous).&n=
bsp;</p></li></ul><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height:=
 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">In <em>Conjuring Scenius</em>, I tried to add so=
me ingredients to the pot, and one in particular seemed to appear before mo=
st of history&#8217;s great Scenia: <strong>catastrophe</strong>.&nbsp;</p>=
